{"tid":876051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強：「中國製造」要盡早變為「中國精造」","createTime":"2018-10-25T10:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T08:53:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c39c25d1ee355c04fa9144f5466d9be5fe665f18","tid":876051,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"李克強：「中國製造」要盡早變為「中國精造」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.903664/popular-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-content%2FNOW.903664%2Fpopular-news&d=tZcJKrdFUBQs1nSAVF51Yf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2564282a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-content/NOW.903664/popular-news</a><br />\n<br />\n國務院總理李克強昨日(24日)應邀在中國工會第十七次全國代表大會上作經濟形勢報告強調，「中國製造」要盡早變為「中國精造」，無論是日常消費品生產，還是高精尖製造，都需要有一大批「身懷絕技」的大國工匠。只要潛心弘揚精益求精的工匠精神，大膽創新能者多得的激勵機制，中國製造就不僅會以性價比風靡全球，更能靠高質量行銷世界。<br />\n<br />\n李克強表示，中國有9億勞動者，1.7億受過高等教育或有專業技能的人才。中國40年的改革開放使廣大勞動者的素質持續提升，技能水平不斷提高。「人口紅利」加速向「人才紅利」轉變，這是中國發展的最大「底氣」。(ta/u)"},{"pid":"a5a8a84dadf941e36dd61e31ae3f43fad1e76790","tid":876051,"uid":9394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"底氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c425670ae926be457bcd0f773fab51a75b7178b0","tid":876051,"uid":30686,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"中國精 造<br />\n識利用地下太多嘅野轉換做其他野<br />\n<br />\n中國贏贏贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7e9555ee9b82f680536dd76adac788b8af5e0","tid":876051,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c425670ae926be457bcd0f773fab51a75b7178b0","tid":876051,"uid":30686,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"中國精 造<br />\n識利用地下太多嘅野轉換做其他野<br />\n<br />\n中國贏贏贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hk